title: Luke Shaw will not feature against Saint-Etienne: Man United fans are absolutely furious
text:
Premier League Championship Scottish Premiership Luke Shaw will not feature against Saint-Etienne: Man United fans are absolutely furious EXPRESS SPORT brings you all the best tweets as fans react to Luke Shaw's omission from Manchester United's travelling squad to face Saint-Etienne. PUBLISHED: 16:50,  05, Tue, Feb 21, 2017 Man United fans furious as Luke Shaw is omitted from squad to face Saint-Etienne Tue, February 21, 2017 Luke Shaw will not be in Manchester United's squad to face Saint-Etienne and fans are not happy Getty Images 1 of 10 Luke Shaw will not be in Man Utd's squad to face Saint-Etienne and fans are mad 
Despite training at Carrington this morning, Shaw has not been included in Manchester United â€™s 20-man squad to face Saint-Etienne on Wednesday. 
Skipper Wayne Rooney, who has been struggling with a muscle injury, has also been omitted from the Europa League squad. 
But the Old Trafford faithful have once again taken to social media to slam Jose Mourinho for his treatment of left-back Shaw .
